free-scan-value-title = What the Free Scan Covers
free-scan-value-subdomains-title = Subdomain Enumeration
free-scan-value-subdomains-desc = Discover subdomains visible to the public via DNS records, certificate transparency logs, and passive sources. Find forgotten dev, staging, and admin endpoints.
free-scan-value-ports-title = Port Discovery
free-scan-value-ports-desc = Identify open ports and running services across your discovered hosts. Detect unexpected services, legacy protocols, and shadow IT before attackers do.
free-scan-value-certs-title = Certificate Transparency
free-scan-value-certs-desc = Check certificate validity, expiry dates, and certificate transparency logs for your domain. Catch expired, misconfigured, or rogue certificates.

free-scan-urgency-title = Attackers Don't Stop at the Free Tier
free-scan-urgency-body = A free scan gives you a snapshot. But your attack surface changes every time you deploy. Continuous ASM monitoring catches new subdomains, exposed services, and certificate changes as they happen — not weeks later.
free-scan-urgency-cta = See Continuous Monitoring Plans

free-scan-faq-title = Free Scan FAQ
free-scan-faq-data-q = What data do you collect during the free scan?
free-scan-faq-data-a = We perform passive reconnaissance only — DNS lookups, certificate transparency log queries, and non-intrusive port checks. We do not store your domain or results after the scan completes. No account is created.
free-scan-faq-safe-q = Is this scan safe? Will it trigger alerts on my infrastructure?
free-scan-faq-safe-a = Yes, it is safe. We use passive techniques that do not send exploit payloads or modify anything on your systems. The scan is comparable to what search engines and certificate monitors already do.
free-scan-faq-difference-q = How is this different from paid ASM monitoring?
free-scan-faq-difference-a = The free scan is a one-time snapshot. Paid continuous monitoring runs 24/7, detects changes as they happen, sends alerts, tracks shadow IT over time, and includes API access and integrations.
free-scan-faq-any-domain-q = Can I scan any domain?
free-scan-faq-any-domain-a = You may scan domains you own or have explicit authorisation to test. We verify domain ownership for paid plans. The free scan uses only publicly available data.
free-scan-faq-where-q = Where does the scan run?
free-scan-faq-where-a = All scanning infrastructure is hosted in the European Union. Data never leaves EU borders. No third-party services outside the EU are involved.

free-scan-final-title = Ready for Continuous Coverage?
free-scan-final-body = The free scan shows you what is exposed right now. Continuous ASM monitoring shows you what changes tomorrow.
free-scan-final-cta = See ASM Plans

